 &lt;span class="dark:text-neutral-300">&lt;strong>Tip 1:&lt;/strong> This can also be found by
&lt;a href="https://docs.astral.sh/ruff/rules/redefined-while-unused/">Ruff&amp;rsquo;s F811 rule&lt;/a>.&lt;/span>
